{"tid":950133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有線］被告和律師合謀法庭上偷證物","createTime":"2018-12-21T09:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T12:44:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"07b9660a0df5689f68e307a06b67da55eaf9dbd6","tid":950133,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"重慶市綦江區法院日前在開庭審理一宗合同糾紛案時，突然發現原告提交的一份文件證物在法庭上離奇消失。<br />\n<br />\n經翻看閉路電視後發現，是其中一被告的律師和另一被告相互串通，偷偷將證物藏匿在長筒靴內。她們事後供稱在開庭前已合謀偷證據。<br />\n<br />\n#若要人不知唔好太低B<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1977262835751526/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1977262835751526%2F&d=3OQGOEmz9Ym3FKyzYyZMxwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d9f6e941\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1977262835751526/</a>"},{"pid":"2e272dc22b011e076cce67724b9f522a2f244e2b","tid":950133,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}